title: Care For Me
notes:
VMP pressing on 180gram vinyl but without OBI, stencil and VMP stamp on the back of the jacket. VMP-043/VMP-RH-014 listed on jacket spine. Comes with glossy heavyweight tip-on style jacket, 10 page lyric booklet, and printed record sleeve.
Available from sabapivot.com store on April 5th, 2021 at 12pm CST. Approximately an hour prior to release, a text password was sent from SabaPivot.com to individuals who texted to a number listed on Saba's social media pages. This hour early release was rumored to be 1000 copies, of which the first 50 were autographed by Saba ("Saba Cares For You" in silver in the lower left corner). The second release, at 12pm, is also rumored to have been another 1000 copies as well.
